      to WSRF.</simpara></listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
  <para>API changes since GT version 4.0.0</para>
  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem><simpara>None</simpara></listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
  <para>Exception changes since GT version 4.0.0</para>
  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem><simpara>None</simpara></listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
  <para>Schema changes since GT version 4.0.0</para>
  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem><simpara>WSDL reflects the port to WSRF from OGSI.</simpara></listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
